| HistoryText             = Headed by [[Medusalith Amaquelin (Earth-616)|Queen Medusa]], the '''New Attilan Security Force''' were the policing division of the [[Inhumans (Inhomo supremis)|Inhumans]] who kept the peace by solving crimes and doing investigations in matters that occured inside the walls of [[New Attilan]], as well as outside on the streets of [[New York City]]. This type of job was something that the [[Inhuman Royal Guard (Earth-616)|Inhuman Royal Guard]] initially didn't do. Originally made up of [[Auran (Earth-616)|Auran]] and her new partner, former [[New York City Police Department (Earth-616)|NYPD]] officer and [[Terrigenesis#Humans|Nuhuman]], [[Frank McGee (Earth-616)|Nur]], they also handled problems that involve covert affairs.{{r|Inhuman Vol 1 7}}
